{"tid":1787741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復連登】請推行動 post！","createTime":"2019-12-18T06:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T12:08:08.000Z","uid":99762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"feba62027ca3d1bfec0e2b7126919ec5fdc7b14a","tid":1787741,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"你知唔知今個星期、下個星期會有咩行動？<br />\n<br />\n連登仍然係一個頗為重要的消息集散地<br />\n好多人，尤其是和理非，都會睇連登，再決定參加咩活動<br />\n<br />\n但係，而家嘅連登<br />\n勁多五毛，勁多鬼，不斷分化、轉移視線<br />\n將啲娛樂 post 不斷推上熱門<br />\n而行動 post 好多都石沉大海<br />\n<br />\n呢度，我希望能夠發起光復連登行動 <br />\n令到多啲人一齊推行動 post <br />\n以後<br />\n逢<span style=\"color: red;\">朝早七點、夜晚九點</span><br />\n光復連登行動會展開<br />\n每次持續半個鐘<br />\n係呢半個鍾，我要所有人瘋狂推行動/行動相關 post<br />\n<br />\n每個人訓醒就睇到，臨訓再睇到<br />\n此舉目的係要令推行動 post 成為一種習慣，並且令所有人都知道未來一星期會有咩行動<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n搞和理非活動時，文宣請加搞手 Channel 名<br />\n並係 Channel /文宣 加活動簡介、目標、注意事項、地形介紹等等俾參加者知道<br />\n呢啲資料對啱啱開始上街嘅人好有用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kdAJFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kdAJFO.jpg&h=cc34275a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgVLmtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgVLmtv.jpg&h=3aff33e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3fd2bee1ab25212680cba116be657bffa3dcca4","tid":1787741,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7164507b157b217969369c4b9931fd84582ecb48","tid":1787741,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ee1f0698bde4b50d10c2bea0a56ba7e23986649","tid":1787741,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e7079e20c73f8de3689ffee22d6165f134222291","tid":1787741,"uid":168138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c1dc3622791c43b1